{"tid":1403423,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"八月五日 遍地開花","createTime":"2019-08-03T18:53:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T08:21:46.000Z","uid":142660,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a48887914cc5745ea61808827a4a9e2278886c3e","tid":1403423,"uid":142660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:53:33.000Z","msg":"東鐵綫  九龍塘  大圍<br />\n西鐵綫  紅磡<br />\n觀塘及將軍澳線  調景嶺<br />\n荃灣及港島線  中環<br />\n<br />\n馬路<br />\n吐露港<br />\n大圍迴旋處<br />\n紅/東/西隧<br />\n元朗大馬路<br />\n城隧<br />\n大欖隧道<br />\n彌敦道<br />\n上水公路<br />\n夏慤道<br />\n觀塘道<br />\n<br />\n有些市民不能主動罷工<br />\n但非常樂意接受被動罷工<br />\n包括我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有車出車<br />\n有力出力<br />\n<br />\n有車既巴絲打<br />\n雙P為記<br />\n死火為由<br />\n<br />\n有力既巴絲打<br />\n如果係地鐵上感到嚴重不適<br />\n請通知路人/朋友<br />\n其他市民應立刻通知車站職員<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"300a65ff0aeec766f8e9ab055bf78288bce1c311","tid":1403423,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:54:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"56212528482c23f28c4e4aabe9d5a63a8ea0835f","tid":1403423,"uid":142660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09891a0b04ccd364401a1039d8d94441eaff5f3e","tid":1403423,"uid":142660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:55:30.000Z","msg":"一齊罷<img src=\"/assets/fac